# Shadcn/ui CLI Usage

When adding new components using the `shadcn/ui` CLI, always use the `shadcn@latest` package name, not the deprecated `shadcn-ui@latest`.

**Correct:**
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component_name>
```

**Incorrect:**
```bash
npx shadcn-ui@latest add <component_name>
```
